SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS

Windows 95/Windows 98
133 MHz Pentium or faster required
16 MB RAM; 32 MB RAM recommended
Minimum 25 MB hard disk space
4X CD-ROM drive or faster
SVGA video card 640 x 480, 256 colors 
Windows compatible sound device
Modem and Internet Service Provider (optional)
Extended Keyboard recommended for Multiplayer games
